OL,6,FClwb Ifor Bach is one of Wales'
OL,7,Fcultural hotspots and the beating
OL,8,Fheart of Cardiff's music scene.
OL,10,FOver the years 'Clwb', as it is often
OL,11,Freferred to, has showcased some of the
OL,12,Fworld's most successful musicians
OL,13,Fearly on in their career.
OL,15,FFrom the likes of The Killers, The
OL,16,FManic Street Preachers and Self
OL,17,FEsteem. It is probably worth
OL,18,Fmentioning the global powerhouse that
OL,19,Fis Coldplay, who came through Clwb
OL,20,FIfor Bach's doors to play their first-
OL,21,Fever set in Wales.
