OL,3,CMeet the Welsh popstar using her music
OL,4,Cto highlight misogyny in the industry
OL,6,FYou sometimes hear about those
OL,7,Funbelievable stories that led young
OL,8,Fartists on their path into the music
OL,9,Findustry, well Twst's story is one of
OL,10,Fthem.
OL,12,FIt all started with her decision to
OL,13,Fmove out of her childhood home in
OL,14,FBarry at the age of 14, to live in an
OL,15,Fabandoned recording studio in
OL,16,FBlackwood, and learn her craft.
