OL,3,CMeet the Welsh popstar using her music
OL,4,Cto highlight misogyny in the industry
OL,6,FTwst (her real name being Chloe Davis)
OL,7,Fsaid: "There was this old abandoned
OL,8,Frecording studio. I mean, it's a long
OL,9,Fstory, but essentially the guy who
OL,10,Fowned it wanted to make his son the
OL,11,Fnext Justin Bieber.
OL,13,F"And he really believed that he was
OL,14,Fgoing to be that. So I sort of just
OL,15,Fbummed around the studio while he was
OL,16,Ftrying to become the next Justin
OL,17,FBieber. And I just lived there for a
OL,18,Fwhile. It was crazy."
