OL,3,CMeet the Welsh popstar using her music
OL,4,Cto highlight misogyny in the industry
OL,6,FTwst also spoke about how this period
OL,7,Fin her life has influenced the music
OL,8,Fshe makes today.
OL,10,FShe said: "I always create from that
OL,11,Fperiod. I think I create from that
OL,12,Fspace that I created for myself when I
OL,13,Fwas that age.
OL,15,F"I feel I was very much exploring
OL,16,Fthese worlds inside my head because I
OL,17,Fwas very isolated there as well. It
OL,18,Fwas a lot of imagination and educating
OL,19,Fmyself through the internet and
OL,20,Fteaching myself all the things that I
OL,21,Fwanted to know."
