OL,4,Cto highlight misogyny in the industry
OL,6,FTwst says it is important for her to
OL,7,Fuse her music as a form of self-
OL,8,Fexpression and to highlight the
OL,9,Finjustices that exist today. A lot of
OL,10,Fher music refers to the misogyny that
OL,11,Fwomen face in society and the music
OL,12,Findustry in particular.
