OL,3,CMeet the Welsh popstar using her music
OL,4,Cto highlight misogyny in the industry
OL,6,FHowever, Twst has tried to find the
OL,7,Fpositive that comes with the internet
OL,8,Fand social media.
OL,10,F"I think there's so many good things
OL,11,Fabout it that it's important to
OL,12,Fhighlight like the sense of community
OL,13,Fthat I found through the internet and
OL,14,Fit has been incredible, steering into
OL,15,Flike the positive side of things and
OL,16,Fhow it's become so community driven
OL,17,Fand how you can connect with so many
OL,18,Fpeople and build communities is
OL,19,Famazing."
